snippet.title: Introducing Spyrazoid for iOS
snippet.description:
Introducing Spyrazoid, a minimalist puzzle game available on the iOS App Store: https://apps.apple.com/us/app/spyrazoid/id1585455563

Spyrazoid is a game built for those who love a fun and strategic challenge. Every board demands a different level of problem solving.  4 Game modes, with 480 pre-programmed boards and infinite randomly generated boards, provide endless casual gameplay.  How many rounds can you complete?

Also follow us on Facebook, Instagram, and Twitter: @spyraverse
